    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总统政治太过激烈？州立法机构也参与选举</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/02/nx-s1-5129659/abortion-election-michigan-arizona-minnesota</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们如此关注总统选举的同时，请记住，这些下级选举可能会导致你所在州的堕胎、医疗保健和刑事司法等政策发生重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/02/nx-s1-5129659/abortion-election-michigan-arizona-minnesota</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
